trans-unit.source: A Haxe String is immutable, it is not possible to modify individual characters. No method of this class changes the state of this String.
trans-unit.target: Haxe 문자열은 변경할 수 없으며 개별 문자를 수정할 수 없습니다. 이 클래스의 어떤 메소드 this String 의 상태를 변경하지 않습니다 .

trans-unit.source: A String buffer is an efficient way to build a big string by appending small elements together.

trans-unit.source: A Vector is a storage of fixed size. It can be faster than Array on some targets, and is never slower.

trans-unit.source: A call to storeExpr(e) is equivalent to storeTypedExpr(typeExpr(e)) without the overhead of encoding and decoding between regular and macro runtime.

trans-unit.source: A closed structure is considered complete. That is, no further fields can be added to it.
